sections.heading: Dumping refuse, rubbish or debris on waterways5-348
sections.text: Dumping refuse, rubbish or debris on waterwaysNo person shall dump, deposit, place, throw or leave refuse, rubbish, debris, filthy or odoriferous objects, substances or other trash on any waterways or the shorelines of any waterways of the state.
